properties.areaDesc: Bays and Waterways from Baffin Bay to Port Aransas; Coastal waters from Baffin Bay to Port Aransas out 20 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 14 at 7:35PM CST until January 15 at 6:00AM CST by NWS Corpus Christi TX
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to one mile or less.

* WHERE...Bays and Waterways from Baffin Bay to Port Aransas and
Coastal waters from Baffin Bay to Port Aransas out 20 NM.

* WHEN...Until 6 AM CST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 AM CST WEDNESDAY
